      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "它们由不同的线交汇而成，各有各的脾气。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "triangle-centers",
      "section_id": "centroid-circum",
      "line_id": "cc-2",
      "filename": "centroid-circum-cc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/triangle-centers/yunxi/centroid-circum-cc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.16,
      "size": 34560,
      "text": "它是三角形的平衡点，用手指顶住这里，纸板恰好不倒。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "triangle-centers",
      "section_id": "incenter-ortho",
      "line_id": "io-1",
      "filename": "incenter-ortho-io-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/triangle-centers/yunxi/incenter-ortho-io-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "内心是三条角平分线的交点，到三条边的距离都相等。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "triangle-centers",
      "section_id": "incenter-ortho",
      "line_id": "io-2",
      "filename": "incenter-ortho-io-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/triangle-centers/yunxi/incenter-ortho-io-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "以内心为圆心，就能画出恰好贴着三条边的内切圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "triangle-centers",
      "section_id": "incenter-ortho",
      "line_id": "io-3",
      "filename": "incenter-ortho-io-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/triangle-centers/yunxi/incenter-ortho-io-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.63,
      "size": 42048,
      "text": "垂心则是三条高线的交点，也就是从每个顶点向对边所作垂线的汇合处。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "triangle-centers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/triangle-centers/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "切换不同形状的三角形，看看四个心如何随之移动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "triangle-centers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/triangle-centers/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "注意钝角三角形里，外心和垂心会跑到三角形外面去。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "triangle-centers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/triangle-centers/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.38,
      "size": 54144,
      "text": "重心、外心、内心、垂心，分别由中线、垂直平分线、角平分线和高线相交而成。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "triangle-centers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/triangle-centers/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.16,
      "size": 34560,
      "text": "外心配外接圆，内心配内切圆，而三心又共处欧拉线。"
    }
